headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Seagate Technology Holdings (STX) After Its 254% One-Year Surge
summary: If you are wondering whether Seagate Technology Holdings at around US$308 per share still offers value after a large increase in price, you are not alone. The stock has posted returns of 11.9% over the past week, 8.0% over the past month, 7.2% year to date, 254.3% over one year and a very large gain over five years. This naturally raises questions about what is already priced in and how much risk you are taking on at these levels. Recent news coverage around Seagate has focused on its role...
